#: ../../api/models.rst:3
msgid "dwh_auditor.models — DWH 監査用内部データモデル (Pydantic)"
msgstr "dwh_auditor.models — Internal data model for DWH auditing (Pydantic)"

#: ../../api/models.rst:5
msgid ""
"``dwh_auditor.models`` パッケージは、各層（Extractor → Analyzer → Reporter）が "
"データを受け渡す際の「型契約」を定義します。 ``dict`` 型を直接受け渡すのではなく Pydantic モデルを使うことで、 "
"静的型チェックとランタイムバリデーションの両方を実現します。"
msgstr ""
"The ``dwh_auditor.models`` package defines the \"type contract\" when each "
"layer (Extractor → Analyzer → Reporter) passes data. By using the Pydantic "
"model rather than passing ``dict`` types directly, we achieve both static "
"type checking and runtime validation."

#: ../../api/models.rst:13
msgid "クエリジョブモデル (``models.job``)"
msgstr "Query job model (``models.job``)"

#: dwh_auditor.models.job:1 of
msgid "BigQuery クエリジョブのデータモデル."
msgstr "BigQuery query job data model."

#: dwh_auditor.models.job.QueryJob:1 of
msgid "BigQuery のクエリジョブ履歴を表すモデル."
msgstr "A model that represents query job history in BigQuery."

#: dwh_auditor.models.job.QueryJob:3 of
msgid ""
"Extractor 層が BQ の INFORMATION_SCHEMA.JOBS から取得し、 Analyzer "
"層に渡す際のデータ契約として機能します。"
msgstr ""
"It serves as the data contract that the Extractor layer retrieves from BQ's "
"INFORMATION_SCHEMA.JOBS and passes it to the Analyzer layer."

#: ../../api/models.rst
msgid "パラメータ"
msgstr "parameters"

#: dwh_auditor.models.job.QueryJob.model_config:1
#: dwh_auditor.models.result.AuditResult.model_config:1
#: dwh_auditor.models.result.CostInsight.model_config:1
#: dwh_auditor.models.result.FullScanInsight.model_config:1
#: dwh_auditor.models.result.ZombieTableInsight.model_config:1
#: dwh_auditor.models.table.TableStorage.model_config:1 of
msgid ""
"Configuration for the model, should be a dictionary conforming to "
"[`ConfigDict`][pydantic.config.ConfigDict]."
msgstr ""
"Configuration for the model, should be a dictionary conforming to "
"[`ConfigDict`][pydantic.config.ConfigDict]."

#: ../../api/models.rst:23
msgid "テーブルストレージモデル (``models.table``)"
msgstr "Table storage model (``models.table``)"

#: dwh_auditor.models.table:1 of
msgid "BigQuery テーブルストレージのデータモデル."
msgstr "BigQuery table storage data model."

#: dwh_auditor.models.table.TableStorage:1 of
msgid "BigQuery テーブルごとのストレージ情報を表すモデル."
msgstr "A model that represents storage information for each BigQuery table."

#: dwh_auditor.models.table.TableStorage:3 of
msgid ""
"Extractor 層が BQ の INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLE_STORAGE から取得し、 Analyzer "
"層（ゾンビテーブル検知）に渡す際のデータ契約として機能します。"
msgstr ""
"It serves as a data contract that the Extractor layer retrieves from BQ's "
"INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLE_STORAGE and passes it to the Analyzer layer (zombie"
" table detection)."

#: dwh_auditor.models.table.TableStorage.full_table_id:1 of
msgid "プロジェクト・データセット・テーブル名を結合した完全修飾名."
msgstr "Fully qualified name concatenated with project dataset table name."

#: ../../api/models.rst:33
msgid "分析結果モデル (``models.result``)"
msgstr "Analysis result model (``models.result``)"

#: dwh_auditor.models.result:1 of
msgid "分析結果のデータモデル."
msgstr "Data model of analysis results."

#: dwh_auditor.models.result:3 of
msgid "Analyzer 層が Reporter 層に渡す診断結果の型定義です。"
msgstr ""
"Type definition for diagnostic results that the Analyzer layer passes to the"
" Reporter layer."

#: dwh_auditor.models.result.CostInsight:1 of
msgid "高コストクエリの分析結果."
msgstr "Analysis results of high cost queries."

#: dwh_auditor.models.result.FullScanInsight:1 of
msgid "フルスキャンと判定されたクエリの分析結果."
msgstr "Analysis results of queries determined to be full scans."

#: dwh_auditor.models.result.ZombieTableInsight:1 of
msgid "使われていないテーブルの分析結果."
msgstr "Analysis results for unused tables."

#: dwh_auditor.models.result.AuditResult:1 of
msgid "Analyzer 層が最終的に出力する総合監査結果レポート."
msgstr ""
"Comprehensive audit result report finally output by the Analyzer layer."
